{
  "stem": "21308.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I always thought that was a bit much.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But we always had freedom to go where you wanted to go.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And-- but as I told you earlier, you had to tell your mother when you got home.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I didn't-- haven't been at church.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I went to chapel.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because you knew damn well that somebody who was in the church would miss you.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And would turn around and say, isn't Teddy well?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Oh, so you had to beat them to it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it was pretty practical, really.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Do you remember the name of that reverend?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes, I do.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember the vicar's name was Bagshaw.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Fallsbury ?] Bagshaw, and the only name-- the only reason I remember it is because in the parish church-- which I have a photograph of which I'd like to show you-- there the pulpit was erected by and paid for by the vicar for his son who was killed in the First World War.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I remember looking there every Sunday.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] [?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Fallsbury ?] Bagshaw was-- gets ground in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then we had a congregational chapel, and the man was named Brewer.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he had a white beard, so he was [INAUDIBLE] Brewer to all of us with his white beard.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But he was a nice chap and a very good preacher.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But I-- I don't remember the names of others.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But I remember them with affection though.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, of course, we covered the Old Testament.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And not just the highlights of it, but we really did cover it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I mean, there was a time when I could go right through Isaiah 40, and I didn't even need to look at the book.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I should stumble a bit now, I think.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
